response.original_title: They Might Be Giants: The Videos 1986-1989
response.overview: This is a compilation video of the first six videos They Might Be Giants created in reverse chronological order. This also is their only release to appear on Laserdisc. Videos included are: (1) "Purple Toupee"; (2) "They'll Need A Crane"; (3) "Ana Ng"; (4) "(She Was A) Hotel Detective"; (5) "Don't Let's Start"; (6) "Put Your Hand Inside The Puppet Head".
response.title: They Might Be Giants: The Videos 1986-1989
